<br>
As for this change, I really hope it will also affect knights, because they need it as well. Right now no knight in his right mind would use 1hs/sheild combo over 2hs, unless they are tanking, then they get the benefit of 1 more stat slot and lose the higher damage they would deal with a 2hs. This is not a very good benefit. =p <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=75721">Woon</a><!--EZCODE LINK END-->  <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://tde.e-slackers.net/">&lt;TDE&gt;</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> <br>
